Package org.transitime.gtfs.writers

For writing GTFS configuration data in CSV format to files.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GtfsExtendedStopTimesWriter
    For writing out extended GTFS stop_times.txt file that contains additional info beyond the usual stop_times.txt file such as statistical info determined when creating the schedule.
    GtfsRoutesWriter
    For writing out the routes.txt GTFS file.
    GtfsShapesWriter
    Writes out a GTFS shapes.txt file.
    GtfsStopsWriter
    For writing out the stops.txt GTFS file.
    GtfsStopTimesWriter
    For writing a GTFS stop_times.txt file.
    GtfsTripsWriter
    For writing out the trips.txt GTFS file.

Package org.transitime.gtfs.writers Description

For writing GTFS configuration data in CSV format to files.
